        "section": "Arithmetical and Numerical Ability",
        "solution": "<b>Solution (EN):</b><br>First, break down the numbers into their prime factors:<br>Number 1: 2<sup>3</sup> &times; 7<sup>2</sup> &times; 14 = 2<sup>3</sup> &times; 7<sup>2</sup> &times; (2 &times; 7) = 2<sup>4</sup> &times; 7<sup>3</sup><br>Number 2: 2<sup>2</sup> &times; 14<sup>2</sup> &times; 18 = 2<sup>2</sup> &times; (2 &times; 7)<sup>2</sup> &times; (2 &times; 3<sup>2</sup>) = 2<sup>2</sup> &times; 2<sup>2</sup> &times; 7<sup>2</sup> &times; 2 &times; 3<sup>2</sup> = 2<sup>5</sup> &times; 3<sup>2</sup> &times; 7<sup>2</sup><br>Number 3: 7<sup>3</sup> &times; 14<sup>2</sup> &times; 18<sup>2</sup> = 7<sup>3</sup> &times; (2 &times; 7)<sup>2</sup> &times; (2 &times; 3<sup>2</sup>)<sup>2</sup> = 7<sup>3</sup> &times; 2<sup>2</sup> &times; 7<sup>2</sup> &times; 2<sup>2</sup> &times; 3<sup>4</sup> = 2<sup>4</sup> &times; 3<sup>4</sup> &times; 7<sup>5</sup><br>To find the LCM, take the highest power of each prime factor present:<br>Highest power of 2 = max(4, 5, 4) = 5.<br>Highest power of 3 = max(0, 2, 4) = 4.<br>Highest power of 7 = max(3, 2, 5) = 5.<br>LCM = 2<sup>5</sup> &times; 3<sup>4</sup> &times; 7<sup>5</sup>.<br><br><b>Solution (HI):</b><br>सबसे पहले, संख्याओं को उनके अभाज्य गुणनखंडों में तोड़ें:<br>संख्या 1: 2<sup>3</sup> &times; 7<sup>2</sup> &times; 14 = 2<sup>3</sup> &times; 7<sup>2</sup> &times; (2 &times; 7) = 2<sup>4</sup> &times; 7<sup>3</sup><br>संख्या 2: 2<sup>2</sup> &times; 14<sup>2</sup> &times; 18 = 2<sup>2</sup> &times; (2 &times; 7)<sup>2</sup> &times; (2 &times; 3<sup>2</sup>) = 2<sup>2</sup> &times; 2<sup>2</sup> &times; 7<sup>2</sup> &times; 2 &times; 3<sup>2</sup> = 2<sup>5</sup> &times; 3<sup>2</sup> &times; 7<sup>2</sup><br>संख्या 3: 7<sup>3</sup> &times; 14<sup>2</sup> &times; 18<sup>2</sup> = 7<sup>3</sup> &times; (2 &times; 7)<sup>2</sup> &times; (2 &times; 3<sup>2</sup>)<sup>2</sup> = 7<sup>3</sup> &times; 2<sup>2</sup> &times; 7<sup>2</sup> &times; 2<sup>2</sup> &times; 3<sup>4</sup> = 2<sup>4</sup> &times; 3<sup>4</sup> &times; 7<sup>5</sup><br>लघुत्तम समापवर्त्य (LCM) ज्ञात करने के लिए, उपस्थित प्रत्येक अभाज्य गुणनखंड की उच्चतम घात लें:<br>2 की उच्चतम घात = max(4, 5, 4) = 5.<br>3 की उच्चतम घात = max(0, 2, 4) = 4.<br>7 की उच्चतम घात = max(3, 2, 5) = 5.<br>LCM = 2<sup>5</sup> &times; 3<sup>4</sup> &times; 7<sup>5</sup>.<br><br><b>Short Trick:</b><br>Expand the bases to prime factors: <br>Term 1 has max power of 7 as 7<sup>3</sup>, Term 2 has max power of 2 as 2<sup>5</sup>, Term 3 has max power of 3 as 3<sup>4</sup> and max power of 7 as 7<sup>5</sup>. Combining highest powers gives 2<sup>5</sup> &times; 3<sup>4</sup> &times; 7<sup>5</sup>.",
