        "section": "Arithmetical and Numerical Ability",
        "solution": "<b>Solution (EN):</b><br>Let the original price of the fuel be 100.<br>Price after 1st month (40% decrease) = 100 &times; (1 - 0.40) = 60.<br>Price after 2nd month (40% decrease) = 60 &times; (1 - 0.40) = 36.<br>Price after 3rd month (45% decrease) = 36 &times; (1 - 0.45) = 19.8.<br>Price after 4th month (55% increase) = 19.8 &times; (1 + 0.55) = 30.69.<br>Overall decrease = 100 - 30.69 = 69.31.<br>Percentage decrease = 69.31%.<br><br><b>Solution (HI):</b><br>माना ईंधन की मूल कीमत 100 है।<br>पहले महीने के बाद कीमत (40% कमी) = 100 &times; (1 - 0.40) = 60.<br>दूसरे महीने के बाद कीमत (40% कमी) = 60 &times; (1 - 0.40) = 36.<br>तीसरे महीने के बाद कीमत (45% कमी) = 36 &times; (1 - 0.45) = 19.8.<br>चौथे महीने के बाद कीमत (55% वृद्धि) = 19.8 &times; (1 + 0.55) = 30.69.<br>कुल कमी = 100 - 30.69 = 69.31.<br>प्रतिशत कमी = 69.31%.<br><br><b>Short Trick:</b><br>Effective multiplier = 0.60 &times; 0.60 &times; 0.55 &times; 1.55 = 0.3069.<br>This means final value is 30.69% of original.<br>Decrease = 100 - 30.69 = 69.31%.",
