        "q_hi": "<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Find the value of </span><img align=\"middle\" alt=\"begin mathsize 16px style fraction numerator square root of 14 space minus space 6 square root of 5 end root space plus space square root of 9 space plus space 4 square root of 5 end root over denominator open parentheses 2 space plus space square root of 3 close parentheses squared space plus space open parentheses square root of 6 space minus space square root of 2 close parentheses squared end fraction end style\" class=\"Wirisformula\" data-mathml=\"«math xmlns=¨http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML¨»«mstyle mathsize=¨16px¨»«mfrac»«mrow»«msqrt»«mn»14«/mn»«mo»§#160;«/mo»«mo»-«/mo»«mo»§#160;«/mo»«mn»6«/mn»«msqrt»«mn»5«/mn»«/msqrt»«/msqrt»«mo»§#160;«/mo»«mo»+«/mo»«mo»§#160;«/mo»«msqrt»«mn»9«/mn»«mo»§#160;«/mo»«mo»+«/mo»«mo»§#160;«/mo»«mn»4«/mn»«msqrt»«mn»5«/mn»«/msqrt»«/msqrt»«/mrow»«mrow»«msup»«mfenced»«mrow»«mn»2«/mn»«mo»§#160;«/mo»«mo»+«/mo»«mo»§#160;«/mo»«msqrt»«mn»3«/mn»«/msqrt»«/mrow»«/mfenced»«mn»2«/mn»«/msup»«mo»§#160;«/mo»«mo»+«/mo»«mo»§#160;«/mo»«msup»«mfenced»«mrow»«msqrt»«mn»6«/mn»«/msqrt»«mo»§#160;«/mo»«mo»-«/mo»«mo»§#160;«/mo»«msqrt»«mn»2«/mn»«/msqrt»«/mrow»«/mfenced»«mn»2«/mn»«/msup»«/mrow»«/mfrac»«/mstyle»«/math»\" loading=\"lazy\" role=\"math\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" style=\"max-width: none;\">.</span>",
        "section": "Arithmetical and Numerical Ability",
        "solution": "<b>Solution (EN):</b><br>The given expression is:<br>[&radic;(14 - 6&radic;5) + &radic;(9 + 4&radic;5)] / [(2 + &radic;3)<sup>2</sup> + (&radic;6 - &radic;2)<sup>2</sup>]<br><br>Numerator:<br>&radic;(14 - 6&radic;5) = &radic;(3<sup>2</sup> + (&radic;5)<sup>2</sup> - 2 &times; 3 &times; &radic;5) = &radic;(3 - &radic;5)<sup>2</sup> = 3 - &radic;5<br>&radic;(9 + 4&radic;5) = &radic;(2<sup>2</sup> + (&radic;5)<sup>2</sup> + 2 &times; 2 &times; &radic;5) = &radic;(2 + &radic;5)<sup>2</sup> = 2 + &radic;5<br>Sum of numerator = 3 - &radic;5 + 2 + &radic;5 = 5.<br><br>Denominator:<br>(2 + &radic;3)<sup>2</sup> = 4 + 3 + 4&radic;3 = 7 + 4&radic;3<br>(&radic;6 - &radic;2)<sup>2</sup> = 6 + 2 - 2&radic;12 = 8 - 4&radic;3<br>Sum of denominator = 7 + 4&radic;3 + 8 - 4&radic;3 = 15.<br><br>Value = Numerator / Denominator = 5 / 15 = 1/3.<br><br><b>Solution (HI):</b><br>दिया गया व्यंजक है:<br>[&radic;(14 - 6&radic;5) + &radic;(9 + 4&radic;5)] / [(2 + &radic;3)<sup>2</sup> + (&radic;6 - &radic;2)<sup>2</sup>]<br><br>अंश:<br>&radic;(14 - 6&radic;5) = &radic;(3<sup>2</sup> + (&radic;5)<sup>2</sup> - 2 &times; 3 &times; &radic;5) = &radic;(3 - &radic;5)<sup>2</sup> = 3 - &radic;5<br>&radic;(9 + 4&radic;5) = &radic;(2<sup>2</sup> + (&radic;5)<sup>2</sup> + 2 &times; 2 &times; &radic;5) = &radic;(2 + &radic;5)<sup>2</sup> = 2 + &radic;5<br>अंश का योग = 3 - &radic;5 + 2 + &radic;5 = 5.<br><br>हर:<br>(2 + &radic;3)<sup>2</sup> = 4 + 3 + 4&radic;3 = 7 + 4&radic;3<br>(&radic;6 - &radic;2)<sup>2</sup> = 6 + 2 - 2&radic;12 = 8 - 4&radic;3<br>हर का योग = 7 + 4&radic;3 + 8 - 4&radic;3 = 15.<br><br>मान = अंश / हर = 5 / 15 = 1/3.<br><br><b>Short Trick:</b><br>Numerator reduces to (3 - &radic;5) + (2 + &radic;5) = 5.<br>Denominator reduces to (7 + 4&radic;3) + (8 - 4&radic;3) = 15.<br>Result = 5/15 = 1/3.",
