        "section": "Arithmetical and Numerical Ability",
        "solution": "<b>Solution (EN):</b><br>Total number of terms = 10<br>Sum of terms = 17 + 4 + 27 + 8 + 26 + 10k + (4k + 17) + (3k &minus; 11) + 27 + 2<br>= (17 + 4 + 27 + 8 + 26 + 17 &minus; 11 + 27 + 2) + (10k + 4k + 3k)<br>= 117 + 17k<br>Average = Sum of terms / Total number of terms<br>27 = (117 + 17k) / 10<br>270 = 117 + 17k<br>17k = 270 - 117 = 153<br>k = 153 / 17 = 9.<br><br><b>Solution (HI):</b><br>पदों की कुल संख्या = 10<br>पदों का योग = 17 + 4 + 27 + 8 + 26 + 10k + (4k + 17) + (3k &minus; 11) + 27 + 2<br>= (17 + 4 + 27 + 8 + 26 + 17 &minus; 11 + 27 + 2) + (10k + 4k + 3k)<br>= 117 + 17k<br>औसत = पदों का योग / कुल पदों की संख्या<br>27 = (117 + 17k) / 10<br>270 = 117 + 17k<br>17k = 270 - 117 = 153<br>k = 153 / 17 = 9.<br><br><b>Short Trick:</b><br>117 + 17k = 27 &times; 10<br>17k = 270 - 117 = 153 &rArr; k = 9.",
