        "q_en": "A man borrowed ₹38,100 at 16.66% per annum compound interest, compounded annually. He promised to clear the loan in three equal annual installments. Find the value of each installment.",
        "q_hi": "एक व्यक्ति ने 16.66% वार्षिक चक्रवृद्धि ब्याज की दर से ₹38,100 उधार लिए, जो वार्षिक रूप से संयोजित होता है। उसने तीन समान वार्षिक किस्तों में ऋण चुकाने का वादा किया। प्रत्येक किस्त का मान ज्ञात कीजिए।",
        "section": "Arithmetical and Numerical Ability",
        "solution": "<b>Solution (EN):</b><br>Rate of interest = 16.66% = 1/6.<br>This means for every ₹6 borrowed, ₹7 has to be paid back. So, the multiplying factor is 7/6.<br>Let the equal annual installment be X.<br>Principal (P) = Sum of present values of all installments.<br>P = X &times; [ (6/7) + (6/7)<sup>2</sup> + (6/7)<sup>3</sup> ]<br>38100 = X &times; [ (6/7) + (36/49) + (216/343) ]<br>Taking LCM as 343:<br>38100 = X &times; [ (294 + 252 + 216) / 343 ]<br>38100 = X &times; [ 762 / 343 ]<br>X = 38100 &times; (343 / 762)<br>X = 50 &times; 343 = ₹17,150.<br>The value of each installment is ₹17,150.<br><br><b>Solution (HI):</b><br>ब्याज दर = 16.66% = 1/6.<br>इसका मतलब है कि उधार लिए गए प्रत्येक ₹6 के लिए ₹7 चुकाने होंगे। अतः, गुणक 7/6 है।<br>माना समान वार्षिक किस्त X है।<br>मूलधन (P) = सभी किस्तों के वर्तमान मूल्यों का योग।<br>P = X &times; [ (6/7) + (6/7)<sup>2</sup> + (6/7)<sup>3</sup> ]<br>38100 = X &times; [ (6/7) + (36/49) + (216/343) ]<br>LCM 343 लेने पर:<br>38100 = X &times; [ (294 + 252 + 216) / 343 ]<br>38100 = X &times; [ 762 / 343 ]<br>X = 38100 &times; (343 / 762)<br>X = 50 &times; 343 = ₹17,150.<br>प्रत्येक किस्त का मान ₹17,150 है।<br><br><b>Short Trick:</b><br>Fraction for 16.66% is 1/6. Multiplier = 7/6.<br>P : I formula for 3 years is P = I &times; (6/7 + 36/49 + 216/343) = I &times; (762/343).<br>Since 38100 = I &times; (762/343), I = 50 &times; 343 = 17150.",
        "topic": "Compound Interest"
    },
